<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Ticket Status Update</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .status-box { 
            background-color: #f0f8ff; 
            border: 1px solid #4CAF50; 
            border-radius: 5px; 
            padding: 15px; 
            margin: 20px 0; 
        }
        .ticket-info { margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; color: #666; }
        .status-approved { color: #4CAF50; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello {{name}}!</h2>
        <p>We have an update regarding your ticket with us.</p>
        
        <div class="status-box">
            <h3>Ticket Status Update</h3>
            <div class="ticket-info">
                <p><strong>Ticket ID:</strong> {{ticket_id}}</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-approved">{{status}}</span></p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>Great news! Your ticket has been <strong>approved</strong> by our admin team. You can now proceed with the next steps:</p>

        <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
        <ol class="steps">
            <li>Log in to your account</li>
            <li>Browse our available packages</li>
            <li>Subscribe to a package that suits your needs</li>
            <li>Complete your vendor profile setup</li>
        </ol>

        <p>Your account is now fully activated and ready to use. If you have any questions about your ticket status or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>Aeration Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>